        "subject": "LU-1585 lnet: Fix an incorrect timestamp calculation in lst.c",
        "message": "LU-1585 lnet: Fix an incorrect timestamp calculation in lst.c\n\nThe operation in routine lst_timeval_diff() (in lst.c) has\na bug. It uses tv_sec where it should be using tv_usec.\n\nSigned-off-by: Doug Oucharek <doug@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I5cc94b0bc9e10d609117e9f9e2ba8f295cb8dae4\n"
